{"id":"eee5e268-f245-4cf3-aeee-ef3549bc907e","name":"Levi and Sterling | Possessive Fated Mates","description":"<p><strong>In a war between werewolves and vampires, your two fated mates find you being bitten by a vampire, and they're about to rip each other apart.</strong></p><hr><p></p><p>Levi Parker and Sterling Knightley are enemies bound by fate, two rivals from opposite worlds, both tethered to the same fragile human woman by an unbreakable bond. One is fire: reckless, furious, and impossible to tame. The other is earth: controlled, commanding, and born to protect. Together, they’re a storm that should never have existed… and yet neither can stay away.</p><p></p><p>When you vanish into a snow-covered forest and are bitten by a vampire, the enemy they were born to hunt, everything changes. Your life hangs by a thread, and it ignites more than their wolves’ fury. It awakens something deeper, darker, and far more dangerous than either of them imagined.</p><p></p><p>Now they’re put into a brutal alliance to keep her alive, but saving you only sharpens the rivalry that could tear them apart. Because neither Levi nor Sterling will ever stop fighting for you.</p><hr><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 32, 32);\">┏</span><span style=\"color: rgb(115, 45, 45);\">━</span><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 55, 55);\">━</span><span style=\"color: rgb(156, 65, 65);\">━</span><span style=\"color: rgb(181, 78, 78);\">━</span><span style=\"color: rgb(207, 84, 84);\">━</span><span style=\"color: rgb(227, 113, 113);\">༻</span><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 59, 81);\">❁</span><span style=\"color: rgb(227, 113, 113);\">༺</span><span style=\"color: rgb(207, 84, 84);\">━</span><span style=\"color: rgb(181, 78, 78);\">━</span><span style=\"color: rgb(156, 65, 65);\">━</span><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 55, 55);\">━</span><span style=\"color: rgb(115, 45, 45);\">━</span><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 32, 32);\">┓</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em